titles.title: A bill to extend the existing suspension of duty on 6-Hydroxy-2-naphthalenesulfonic acid, and its sodium, potassium, and ammonium salts.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S7093)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 6/10/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1995, the suspension of duty on 6-hydroxy-2-naphthalene-sulfonic acid, and its sodium, potassium, and ammonium salts.
